Package: QuASAR2
Type: Package
Title: Quantitative Allele Specific Analysis of Reads v2
Version: 0.3.0
Date: 2026-05-14
Author: Roger Pique-Regi, Chris Harvey, G Moyerbrailean, C Kalita, et al.
Maintainer: Roger Pique-Regi <rpique@gmail.com>
Description: Joint genotyping, error estimation, and Allele Specific Expression
    inference for multiple RNA-Seq samples. Includes fitQuasar2CR(), a beta-
    binomial GLM with Cox-Reid profile-likelihood dispersion estimation,
    empirical-Bayes shrinkage across SNPs, and design-matrix based LRT and
    Wald inference.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports:
    MASS,
    stats
Suggests:
    locfit,
    numDeriv,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Encoding: UTF-8
